'''法拉利恩佐'''（{{lang-en|'''-{zh-cn:Enzo;zh-tw:Enzo}- Ferrari'''}}）是由[[意大利|意大利]]汽车制造商[[法拉利|法拉利]]所设计、生产的一款超级跑车，以法拉利公司创始人[[恩佐·法拉利|-{zh-cn:恩佐·法拉利;zh-tw:恩佐·法拉利}-]]的名字命名。2002年上市，以慶祝車廠創立55週年，限量生产399台，另外还有一台特别款赠送给了[[教宗|教宗]]後拍賣，所得收益撥捐予[[2004年南亞海嘯|2004年南亞海嘯]]災民。<ref>[http://xk.cn.yahoo.com/articles/071226/1/79cw.html 史上最强的法拉利Enzo大聚会] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080422174059/http://xk.cn.yahoo.com/articles/071226/1/79cw.html |date=2008-04-22 }}</ref>

== 簡介 ==
恩佐由曾任職[[賓尼法利納|賓尼法利納]]的[[日本|日本]][[設計師|設計師]][[奥山清行|奥山清行]]設計，曾經以F60作為初步命名，採用了大量的一級方程式賽車設計概念及技術，[[一級方程式賽車|一級方程式賽車]]手[[迈克尔·舒马赫|迈克尔·舒马赫]]有部份參與研製，引擎為6公升V12型，最大馬力以及扭力分別為660PS/7800rpm以及67kgm/5500rpm，配上6前速F1半自動變速箱，0-100km/h只需3.6秒（官方數據，非官方數據更短，達到3.2秒）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.motortrend.com/roadtests/coupes/112_0308_2003_ferrari_enzo/specs_price.html |title=2003 Ferrari Enzo Engine, Chassis, Dimensions, Price & Performance Data - Road Test Review |publisher=Motor Trend |date= |accessdate=2012-09-02 |archive-date=2015-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151106191742/http://www.motortrend.com/roadtests/coupes/112_0308_2003_ferrari_enzo/specs_price.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，極速可達到355km/h<ref name="RSsportscars">{{cite web | title = 2002 Ferrari Enzo | publisher = RSsportscars | url = http://www.rssportscars.com/cars/2002-ferrari-enzo | accessdate = 2015-02-17 | archive-date = 2019-08-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190812055253/http://www.rssportscars.com/cars/2002-ferrari-enzo | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://paultan.org/archives/2006/06/26/vw-phases-out-automatics-makes-way-for-dsg/|title=Volkswagen makes way for DSG|accessdate=2006-08-11|publisher=Paul Tan|archive-date=2007-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071124024636/http://paultan.org/archives/2006/06/26/vw-phases-out-automatics-makes-way-for-dsg/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url=http://auto.howstuffworks.com/enzo2.htm| title=Turning Point| publisher=[[How_Stuff_Works|How Stuff Works]]| first=Edward| last=Grabianowski| accessdate=2007-03-25| archive-date=2011-10-16| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111016102203/http://auto.howstuffworks.com/enzo2.htm| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

為防止不良炒風，購買恩佐的先決條件就是至少擁有3輛其他法拉利車型，擁有F40或者F50則有優先權。恩佐原本生產349台，可是由於符合購車條件的買家超出預定的產量，所以增至399台<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.autoblog.com/2005/12/08/ferrari-donates-proceeds-of-400th-enzo-to-pope|title=Ferrari donates proceeds of 400th Enzo to Pope|last=Ahlgrim|accessdate=2005-12-08|publisher=[[Autoblog.com|Autoblog.com]]|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111213240/https://www.autoblog.com/2005/12/08/ferrari-donates-proceeds-of-400th-enzo-to-pope/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.luxurylaunches.com/auctions/1m_ferrari_enzo_donated_to_st_jude_childrens_research_hospital.php|title=$1M Ferrari Enzo donated to St. Jude Children’s Research Hospital|last=Ahlgrim|accessdate=2006-09-14|publisher=[[luxurylaunches.com|luxurylaunches.com]]|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120094909/https://luxurylaunches.com/auctions/1m_ferrari_enzo_donated_to_st_jude_childrens_research_hospital.php|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sportscarmarket.com/profiles/2006/January/Ferrari/index.html|title=2005 Enzo Ferrari|last=Ahlgrim|first=Steve|accessdate=2007-03-04|publisher=[[Sports_Car_Market|Sports Car Market]]|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070303150237/http://www.sportscarmarket.com/profiles/2006/January/Ferrari/index.html|archivedate=2007-03-03}}</ref>。

== 榮譽和負評 ==
美國汽車雜誌《Sports Car International》，於2004年將法拉利Enzo評定為2000年代頂級跑車的第三位。另一美國汽車雜誌《Motor Trend》，認為它在史上十大最好法拉利中排行第四。《[[彭博商業周刊|彭博商業周刊]]》（{{lang|en|Bloomberg Businessweek}}）則大唱反調，認為它的是過去50年最醜的50款汽車（{{lang|en|Fifty Ugliest Cars of the Past 50 Years}}）之一，批評它的曲線多餘，角度浮誇，尤其是那個V形的{{link-en|車頭引擎蓋|Hood (vehicle)|車頭蓋}}、兜風的車門和球狀擋風玻璃更加其醜無比<ref>{{cite web |url=http://images.businessweek.com/ss/09/10/1028_50_ugliest_cars_of_past_50_years/40.htm |title=Fifty Ugliest Cars of the Past 50 Years: Chevrolet Avalanche - BusinessWeek |publisher=Images.businessweek.com |date= |accessdate=2012-09-02 |archive-date=2015-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150113074627/http://images.businessweek.com/ss/09/10/1028_50_ugliest_cars_of_past_50_years/40.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

